    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>&quot;Last Shift&quot; is a first person psychological horror videogame with a complete linear story</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>and an average time of completion of 30-40 minutes.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Story</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In it we take on the role of Mark Thompson, who, due to certain issues, loses his job and has to accept a night cleaning job at an office. A relatively simple task, until Mark begins to experience strange occurrences in the office that lead to his disappearance. Months later, a detective delves into this case to uncover what secrets that place hides.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is primarily a first-person walking simulator with elements of exploration and interaction with different objects in various situations.¡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323670/extras/0536ffc5fe49a596ba994ff210a3a80b.poster.avif?t=1765497284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323670/extras/0536ffc5fe49a596ba994ff210a3a80b.webm?t=1765497284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323670/extras/0536ffc5fe49a596ba994ff210a3a80b.mp4?t=1765497284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Note: This game does not include a save system. It’s designed to be completed in a single session</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Game Features</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unsettling and immersive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover who is behind Mark's disappearance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different tasks to complete in each location</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the mistery if you can</p></li></ul>",
